data.description: Great home, great location! Recent updates in kitchen and bathrooms as well as new flooring downstairs. Kitchen includes a eat-in breakfast area, updated cabinet fronts, and plenty of counter space. Kitchen appliances convey. HVAC and water heater also recently replaced. All bedrooms are upstairs. Primary bedroom has a window seat & walk in closet. Close to the medical center, USAA, and shopping.
